  "prompt": "How much is hootsuite?",
  "response": "Hootsuite offers several pricing plans to cater to different needs. As of my last update, the plans were as follows:\n\n1. **Professional**: $49/month (for one user, up to 10 social profiles)\n2. **Team**: $99/month (for three users, up to 20 social profiles)\n3. **Business**: $599/month (for five users, up to 35 social profiles, with additional features like employee advocacy and priority support)\n4. **Enterprise**: Custom pricing (for larger organizations needing advanced features and dedicated support)\n\nPlease note that these prices are subject to change, and Hootsuite may offer different plans or promotions at different times. It's best to check their official website for the most current pricing and features.",
